cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with image segmentation using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of interactive training and feedback loops also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the segmentation of neuronal structures implies a connection to neuroscience (cs.NE) and medical imaging (cs.MM).
